---
description: Pin all dependencies except peer dependencies
globs: ["package.json", "*/package.json", "**/package.json"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Always pin dependencies to exact versions (no `^` or `~` prefix)
- Exception: peer dependencies may use version ranges
- Examples:
  - ✅ Good: `"typescript": "5.7.2"`
  - ❌ Bad: `"typescript": "^5.7.2"`
  - ✅ Good (peer): `"react": "^18.0.0"` (peer dependencies only)
- This ensures reproducible builds and prevents unexpected breaking changes
